        " رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \"نِعْمَ اَلْإِدَامُ اَلْخَلُّ مَا أَقْفَرَ بَيْتٌ فِيهِ خَلٌّ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4267 - The Messenger of Allah (swt) (peace be upon him and his family) said: \"What an excellent condiment vinegar is! A house that has vinegar will never be destitute.\""
        ]
      }
